pr_title: ghostscript filters(gstopxl, gstoraster, gstopdf) now PPD file independent.
pr_body:
1. Ghostscript (gstopxl, gstoraster, gstopdf) now PPD file independent.
2. Updated cupsRasterParseIPPOptions to support Job-attrs.
3. Made cupsRasterPrepareHeader PPD file independent.

I will soon write an alternative function ppdRasterInterpretPPD which uses printer-attrs instead of PPD file and will make its use wherever needed.
Thanks

pr_body:
issue #97 
I am creating this new clean PR as [old one](https://github.com/OpenPrinting/cups/pull/112) was getting messy with conflicts and unnecessary commits.
As far as I have self tested, we are getting all the libs using `pkg-config cups --static --libs` which we are getting in `cups-config --static --libs`.
The default dir of installation of `cups.pc` file is `/usr/lib/pkgconfig` although we can change this behaviour using `--with-pkgconfpath=PATH` or `--prefix=PATH`.
The `autoconf` version I used is 2.70
@michaelrsweet  please review it.
Thanks

solved issue [#93](https://github.com/OpenPrinting/cups/issues/93)
